October 30, 1990, Tuesday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<P>
BRUCE JOEL RUBIN 
</P>
<SECTION>
<P>
Calendar; Part F; Page 1; Column 4; Entertainment Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
<P>
1748 words 
</P>
