<P>
JAPAN FISHING BOAT SEIZED 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Associated Press 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
JAKARTA, Indonesia 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
A Japanese boat has been seized for alleged illegal fishing off Indonesia's 
easternmost province of Irian Jaya, the latest in series of foreign vessels 
captured by authorities, an official report said Monday. 
</P>
